{"id":945809319,"question_id":13,"lang":"java","lang_name":"Java","time":"1 year, 4 months","timestamp":1683429185,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"4 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/945809319/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Roman to Integer","memory":"42.9 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    public int romanToInt(String s) {\n        int sum = 0;\n        \n        for(int i = 0; i < s.length(); i++){\n            if (s.charAt(i) == 'I') {\n                if (i < s.length() - 1){\n                    if (s.charAt(i + 1) == 'V' || s.charAt(i + 1) == 'X') {\n                        sum -= 2;\n                    }\n                }\n                sum++;\n            }\n            \n            else if (s.charAt(i) == 'X') {\n                if (i < s.length() - 1){\n                    if (s.charAt(i + 1) == 'L' || s.charAt(i + 1) == 'C') {\n                        sum -= 20;\n                    }\n                }  \n                sum += 10;\n            }\n            \n            else if (s.charAt(i) == 'C') {\n                if (i < s.length() - 1){\n                    if (s.charAt(i + 1) == 'D' || s.charAt(i + 1) == 'M') {\n                        sum -= 200;\n                    }\n                }   \n                sum += 100;\n            }\n\n            else if (s.charAt(i) == 'V') {\n                sum += 5;\n            }\n\n            else if (s.charAt(i) == 'L') {\n                sum += 50;\n            }\n\n            else if (s.charAt(i) == 'D') {\n                sum += 500;\n            }\n\n            else if (s.charAt(i) == 'M'){\n                sum += 1000;\n            }\n        } \n        return sum;\n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"roman-to-integer","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
